PrecisAppointment of an Administrator, namely Mr. Justice THOMAS C. WAKELING, a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Saskatchewan, who shall temporarily execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor of Saskatchewan over the course of an eight day period in January 1991 (15th to the 22nd).
